item.dc:creator: @patargangstar patargangstar
item.description:
@patargangstar wrote:

[quote=“holmzy, post:8, topic:398559”]hey guys, i got my pi working and everything last night, i wanted to make myself owner, but i got no char files :S what do i do??

pm or email me please thanks.[/quote][quote=“holmzy, post:10, topic:398559”]hey guys, can any1 tell me how i can make my PI server a spawn server?[/quote]

holy fuck dude quit topic stealing asshole

OT: when your trying to log onto your own server you log into localhost, meaning you’ll use a seperate type of client then your players, make a copy of your client go into client.java look for server = thats where your ip is, for your client change the ip to 127.0.0.1 or 0.0.0.0 thats localhost meaning you are logging in from your own computer that is hosting then on your other client use your normal server ip and it should work.

feel free to pm me for any help or to ask any follow up questions

pm or email me please thanks.[/quote]

go to your source file
data/characters/USERNAME HERE
now head to the commands.java and find the owners name… switch it with yours if you cant spawn by just changing your right to 3
